Laws 2026, LB905, § 38. The Revisor of Statutes has pursuant to section 49-769 correlated LB716, section 2, with LB905, section 38, to reflect all amendments.Changes made by LB716 became effective July 18, 2026. Changes made by LB905 became operative July 1, 2026.>
